Hi Chris,

Have you looked at your air filter? For a while I used to get a 
fair-sized blue cloud at start-up until an overdue tune-up where I 
discovered oil deposits in the air box . After replacing the air filter 
the problem disappeared.

YMMV.

Happy trails,

